1
00:00:01,075 --> 00:00:04,477
TAPE NUMBER FOUR MR MR ISAAC DANIELS.

2
00:00:05,007 --> 00:00:10,941
OK, MR DANIELS ir zent ir zent mir ayer froy un mit der kind,

3
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:19,124
ikh bin ikh bin mit mayn froy bay t- akht ts- tsen teg, ven ikh bin gekumen.

4
00:00:19,958 --> 00:00:31,646
mayn froy vert krank, krigt a tifus. m'nemt ir tsu in a HOSPITAL.

5
00:00:33,593 --> 00:00:43,357
s'vayl di in mitn der nakht ho'mir nisht gevust vos s'iz geshen. m'hot hot ongehoybn tsu zingen fun groyse hits,

6
00:00:43,954 --> 00:00:49,635
in der fri hob ikh gerufn a dokter un der dokter hot gezogt az zi hot a tifus, m'darf ir tsunemen in HOSPITAL arayn.

7
00:00:49,945 --> 00:00:54,579
m'hot ir tsugenumen in HOSPITAL arayn, ikh hob shoyn nisht gekent geyn arbetn.

8
00:00:54,670 --> 00:00:56,452
gemuzt zikh opgebn mitn kind.

9
00:00:58,703 --> 00:01:00,958
MEANWHILE iz mayn bruder gekumen.

10
00:01:01,808 --> 00:01:07,843
un er hot nisht gekent zayn mit mir, er hot gezen di situatsye, iz er avek keyn Byalistok.

11
00:01:08,423 --> 00:01:12,399
ikh hob im azoy lib gehat az az ikh hob gekhalesht far im.

12
00:01:14,582 --> 00:01:22,238
SO hot genumen a a gevise tsayt, epes ikh gedenk nisht genoy vifl vokhn zi iz geven in HOSPITAL.

13
00:01:22,648 --> 00:01:24,819
zi iz aheymgekumen fun HOSPITAL.

14
00:01:25,838 --> 00:01:28,684
un ir zent dortn geblibn bli- biz may?

15
00:01:29,027 --> 00:01:37,576
biz MAY. MAY iz aroys a gezets az ale di velkhe zenen gekumen fun yener zayt

16
00:01:39,338 --> 00:01:43,432
muzn avek fun danen, vayl dos iz a militerishe shtot.

17
00:01:44,299 --> 00:01:49,051
muzn avekforn fun danen ammeynstn akhtsn kilometer.

18
00:01:50,020 --> 00:01:53,676
di velkhe voynen zenen aynvoyners fun dortn,

19
00:01:54,002 --> 00:01:57,467
kenen MOVEn di hayzer, iberMOVEn,

20
00:01:57,467 --> 00:02:01,151
vayl s'gevezn di MOST iz gevezn HILLS un hayzer.

21
00:02:01,208 --> 00:02:04,999
kenen zey MOVEn, m'hot zey gegebn epes a mayl avek fun danet.

22
00:02:07,013 --> 00:02:13,015
SO ikh bin avekgeforn mit di froy mitn kind keyn Simyatitsh.

23
00:02:14,117 --> 00:02:17,115
a s'geven a akhtsn kilometer fun danen dortn ahin.

24
00:02:17,779 --> 00:02:23,764
un dortn hob ikh geRENT a ROOM, m'iz dortn geshtanen.

25
00:02:28,782 --> 00:02:31,223
ober keyn gelt hob ikh nisht gehat.

26
00:02:32,562 --> 00:02:34,665
ikh hob kimat nisht gehat fun vanen tsu lebn.

27
00:02:36,122 --> 00:02:40,351
hob ikh zikh bakent mit a tsvey FAMILIES,

28
00:02:41,252 --> 00:02:46,899
eyn FAMILY iz geven fun Sokolov, hot er geheysn Ruvnshteyn,

29
00:02:47,142 --> 00:02:50,156
di tsveyte gedenk ikh nisht dem tsvey- dem un dem tsveytn nomen.

30
00:02:50,415 --> 00:02:56,804
iz dort geven a BOY vos er iz gevezn epes yinger fun mir.

31
00:02:58,262 --> 00:03:00,855
iz m'hot zikh azoy gut bafrayndet,

32
00:03:01,452 --> 00:03:07,588
az zey flegn, di tsveyte, Rubnshteyn, di tsveyte FAMILY,

33
00:03:07,678 --> 00:03:11,908
iz iz hobn gekrign epes azoy tsu mir tsutroy

34
00:03:12,184 --> 00:03:17,139
un vegn di politishe lage vos ven,

35
00:03:17,348 --> 00:03:21,425
vos vet zayn, ho'mir shtendik geredt, vos vet zayn fun undz, vos vet do zayn?

36
00:03:23,490 --> 00:03:27,129
un fregn mikh an eytse. zey zenen shoyn eltere mentshn,

37
00:03:27,287 --> 00:03:30,065
un un un sokhrim un azoy vayter,

38
00:03:30,966 --> 00:03:32,985
zog ikh, "mayn meynung iz azoy.

39
00:03:33,345 --> 00:03:37,422
do, oyb mir veln blaybn do, veln mir umkumen.

40
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:44,038
vayl a milkhome mit Rusland di daytshn iz umfarmaydlekh, oysgeshlosn, s'muz zayn,

41
00:03:46,069 --> 00:03:52,677
di eyntsike zakh iz oyb di rusn veln makhn ergetsh a lager vayt avek un undz farshikn,

42
00:03:52,903 --> 00:03:54,922
ho'mir a CHANCE tsu blaybn lebn."

43
00:03:58,101 --> 00:04:01,639
zey hobn getrakht ahin aher, zey zogn az s'iz meglekh s'iz an IDEA.

44
00:04:02,438 --> 00:04:05,452
BUT, ver veyst tsi di rusn veln makhn a lager?

45
00:04:06,302 --> 00:04:08,355
BUT dervayl iz dokh nishto fun vanen tsu lebn.

46
00:04:09,643 --> 00:04:16,387
zogt er mir Rubnshteyn, "nem mayn zun, ikh vel aykh gebn gelt,

47
00:04:17,017 --> 00:04:20,588
in Byalistok iz zeyer tayer, EGGS, puter, dos.

48
00:04:21,051 --> 00:04:24,436
koyfts do ayn, un forts ahin farkoyft dos.

49
00:04:24,848 --> 00:04:35,642
un dortn zolt ir koyfn skhoyre far LADIES' DRESSES. di geblumte skhoyres."

50
00:04:37,723 --> 00:04:41,311
azoy ho'mir getun. s'nisht geven nisht geven gring ontsukumen mit der ban,

51
00:04:41,875 --> 00:04:46,813
vayl di rusn hobn gezukht a yene mayse. m'hot zikh adurkh geshvartst.

52
00:04:48,321 --> 00:04:51,453
aribergekumen, m'hot farkoyft take far a gants gutn prayz,

53
00:04:52,337 --> 00:04:56,229
hob ikh gehert az in in a STORE

54
00:04:56,303 --> 00:05:03,016
di rusn gibn aroys tsu draysik YARD MATERIALS

55
00:05:03,016 --> 00:05:08,194
ALL KINDS geblumte far VERY VERY CHEAP. VERY VERY VERY.

56
00:05:09,178 --> 00:05:15,027
m'darf shteyn a reye. ANYWAY, ikh bin gegangen, ikh mitn mit mitn mit mayn khaver,

57
00:05:15,591 --> 00:05:18,347
un m'hot gekoyft, m'hot gekrign dortn,

58
00:05:18,347 --> 00:05:22,824
un m'hot nokh a bisl tsugekoyft. m'iz aheymgekumen, s'gut gevezn.

59
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:26,570
nu az s'gelungen eyn mol, darf men geyn nokh a mol.

60
00:05:27,117 --> 00:05:28,866
gegangen dos tsveyte mol,

61
00:05:30,947 --> 00:05:36,560
shteyen a gantse reye oysgeshtelt mentshn vartn far der ban,

62
00:05:36,583 --> 00:05:40,965
un yeder eyner hot hot vos tsu fark- vos er hot gekoyft peklekh.

63
00:05:42,135 --> 00:05:46,921
un mayn khaver zog ikh, "du gey koyf TICKETS, ikh vel do shteyn."

64
00:05:47,468 --> 00:05:49,234
ikh gehat geRENT sheyn pekl,

65
00:05:50,488 --> 00:05:56,136
vi ikh gib a kuk, ze ikh fun yener zayt geyen di day- di rusn,

66
00:05:56,209 --> 00:05:58,821
un m'konfiskirt altsding, m'nemt tsu.

67
00:05:58,821 --> 00:06:00,759
un di mentshn nemt men tsu in JAIL arayn.

68
00:06:03,752 --> 00:06:05,444
trakht mir, mayn kapore iz es.

69
00:06:05,444 --> 00:06:07,863
ikh loz lign dos pekl, gey avek in der zayt.

70
00:06:08,055 --> 00:06:13,094
gey ariber oyf der anderer zayt, un ikh kuk vos vet zayn.

71
00:06:13,472 --> 00:06:18,562
un er nemt greyt m'nemt tsu altsding. mayn pekl lozt men iber.

72
00:06:19,362 --> 00:06:21,617
az keyner iz nishto, s'ligt azoy.

73
00:06:22,129 --> 00:06:27,894
mayn khaver kumt aroys mit di TICKETS, zog ikh, "gey avek. gey gornisht tsu tsum pekl. zoln zey UNK."

74
00:06:28,035 --> 00:06:33,474
ANYWAY s'mir gelungen. m'iz arayn in der ban arayn mitn pekl.

75
00:06:35,595 --> 00:06:47,165
un MEANWHILE, iz zayne eltern hobn geMOVEt nisht vayt fun danen in an ort lebn a mil.

76
00:06:47,712 --> 00:06:50,035
s'geven epes bay a tsen kilometer.

77
00:06:50,985 --> 00:06:57,645
nor ven ikh for krik, muz men optretn dem veg do, un m'hot opgetretn bay zey.

78
00:07:00,165 --> 00:07:06,541
zogt er undz, "kinderlekh, ir kent mit di skhoyre nisht araynforn keyn keyn Simertitsh.

79
00:07:06,541 --> 00:07:13,004
ale vegn zenen bashtelt mit zelner. m'revidirt, m'nemt tsu, s'geferlekh.

80
00:07:13,004 --> 00:07:17,068
epes darf forkumen. azoy fil militer, UNK."

81
00:07:18,762 --> 00:07:23,481
m'hot ibergelozt di skhoyre dortn, un er als a kind iz er geblibn mit di eltern,

82
00:07:23,622 --> 00:07:25,860
un ikh bin arayngeforn do in UNK.

83
00:07:27,469 --> 00:07:29,673
un ikh hob dertseylt mayn froy vos s'UNK.

84
00:07:29,848 --> 00:07:34,045
zogt zi, "du host gornisht keyn anung vifl zelner vifl militer do iz do."

85
00:07:35,788 --> 00:07:39,951
shoyn zi hot iz ongekumen fraytik zi m'hot opgekokht epes dort, m'hot opgegesn.

86
00:07:40,682 --> 00:07:45,452
efsher tsvelef bay nakht, eynse bay nakht, m'klapt. zelner.

87
00:07:46,318 --> 00:07:50,446
m'kumt arayn, UNK, farnem zikh.

88
00:07:51,381 --> 00:07:55,360
andere pletser iz geven s'arayngekumen a zelner, er iz geven a guter,

89
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,478
hot er gezogt, vos du host nem dikh mit.

90
00:07:57,478 --> 00:07:59,896
mir hobn nisht gelozn onrirn azoy groys.

91
00:08:00,072 --> 00:08:02,918
ikh hob gehat dortn a bisl produktn, EGG, dos dort.

92
00:08:03,801 --> 00:08:05,465
nisht gelozt rirn gornisht.

93
00:08:05,843 --> 00:08:09,501
m'hot undz tsugenumen, aroyfgezetst oyf TRUCKS,

94
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:09,409
aykh?

95
00:08:09,501 --> 00:08:11,084
un di froy mitn kind,

96
00:08:10,533 --> 00:08:11,583
mitn kind.

97
00:08:11,226 --> 00:08:14,527
ye, tsugefirt tsu der tsu der ban.

98
00:08:15,242 --> 00:08:19,061
dervayle m'hot, eyder m'iz gegangen un arayn in di ban arayn, m'hot

99
00:08:19,061 --> 00:08:24,500
dos kind iz gegangen hot zi zikh epes gegebn a drey dos fisl, un s'iz aroys fun beyn.

100
00:08:25,772 --> 00:08:28,803
un dos kind veynt, shrayt, zi ken nisht geyn.

101
00:08:29,333 --> 00:08:34,153
ikh hob gevust dortn, in yenem vagon, hob ikh gevust s'dortn do a dokter.

102
00:08:34,648 --> 00:08:37,916
vil ikh nemen mitn kind loyfn tsum dokter, er lozt mir nisht.

103
00:08:38,158 --> 00:08:43,214
ANYWAY, ikh hob nisht gekukt, er er shteyt mit der biks, er geyt mikh shisn. zog ikh, du kenst shisn.

104
00:08:43,238 --> 00:08:44,582
un ikh bin gelofn tsu,

105
00:08:44,672 --> 00:08:49,188
un der dokter hot genumen dos fisl, er hot es gegebn a drey, er hot krik arayngezetst in glid arayn.

106
00:08:50,443 --> 00:08:52,979
m'hot arayngezetst in vagon arayn, m'hot ongehoybn tsu forn.

107
00:08:52,970 --> 00:08:54,090
vu hin?

108
00:08:54,060 --> 00:08:55,111
veyst nisht.

109
00:08:56,029 --> 00:08:57,525
keyner hot nisht gevust vu.

110
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:05,558
dervayl m'hot men undz arayngenumen epes, di ershtn tog hot men arayngegebn epes broyt, a bisl zup.

111
00:09:05,766 --> 00:09:09,568
vi zey hobn gezogt zey ebn far ale statsyes ebn zey gibn vaser.

112
00:09:09,568 --> 00:09:11,400
s'nisht ongehoybn, s'lozt zikh oys.

113
00:09:12,313 --> 00:09:16,493
der vos er hot gefirt dem gantsn shalon, iz geven a kapitan.

114
00:09:18,051 --> 00:09:22,230
eyn mol iz men gegangen, m'hot gedorfn brengen, m'hot gezogt m'get zup

115
00:09:22,573 --> 00:09:27,782
oyf der statsye un yeder eyner darf bre- nemen farn gantsn vagon, di zup.

116
00:09:28,294 --> 00:09:30,414
m'gey- ver geyt? ikh gey.

117
00:09:31,483 --> 00:09:33,552
tref ikh dem kapitan, red ikh mit im.

118
00:09:34,723 --> 00:09:42,125
zogt er tsu mir, "ikh vuntsh dir eyn zakh, az do vu du forst zolst lang nisht darfn zayn."

119
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,174
"vu fort men?"

120
00:09:45,174 --> 00:09:47,424
"UNK. ikh veys nisht."

121
00:09:47,430 --> 00:09:48,656
er hot mir nisht gevolt zogn.

122
00:09:50,704 --> 00:09:53,899
mit mir iz geforn nokh a FAMILY,

123
00:09:53,899 --> 00:09:56,841
in vagon lebn mir, m'iz geshlofn derlebn,

124
00:09:57,201 --> 00:10:03,236
shoyn a yid an elterer, er iz geforn mit a zun un a tokhter un an eydem.

125
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:09,733
un dem eydem's froy iz geblibn in der heym. in Sokolov.

126
00:10:11,342 --> 00:10:17,006
iz far tog, geven a kleyn fentsterl aroystsukukn fun vagon,

127
00:10:18,953 --> 00:10:22,811
vekt er mikh oyf. der yid hot gekukt aroys do, vekt er mikh oyf.

128
00:10:23,037 --> 00:10:27,334
zogt er, Yi- Yi- Yitskhokl, hot er mikh gerufn, "Yitskhokl, s'nisht gut."

129
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,344
"vos heyst s'nisht gut? vu fort men?"

130
00:10:31,344 --> 00:10:35,889
"m'fort oyf Sibir. hakn holts."

131
00:10:37,363 --> 00:10:38,926
"fun vanen veystu?"

132
00:10:39,557 --> 00:10:44,309
"mayn tate iz geven a vald soykher, er flegt koyfn in Rusland holts.

133
00:10:44,485 --> 00:10:49,963
un er hot undz oysgemoshlt, forn mir in dem zelbn veg vi mayn foter hot undz gemoshlt."

134
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:59,919
un m'iz ongekumen nokh tsvey vokhn ze'mir ongekumen oyf a plats,

135
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:06,889
dos iz shoyn gevezn in JULY. MIDDLE OF JULY.

136
00:11:08,076 --> 00:11:15,748
hot men undz aroysge- t- t- fun di vagonen aroys aroysgelozt oyf a leydikn plats.

137
00:11:17,070 --> 00:11:20,996
un dortn iz geven a groysn shayer, a ir veyst vos a shayer iz?

138
00:11:22,048 --> 00:11:28,539
a a a shap. a shap iz nisht vu m'arbet. a SHOP.

139
00:11:29,001 --> 00:11:34,445
vi vi vi vi fayer-layter zenen do aza min aza min sha- aza min shteyger BUILDING.

140
00:11:35,363 --> 00:11:37,688
dortn hot men gedorfn nekhtikn INSIDE.

141
00:11:37,688 --> 00:11:41,162
ober in droysn hot men gekent zitsn in droysn. shteyner.

142
00:11:44,425 --> 00:11:47,102
un s'geven eyner a komendant vos hot undz gehitn.

143
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:55,213
iz azoy. ver s'hot gehat produktn vos m'hot ikh zog aykh vos di da- di di di zelner hot men derloybt,

144
00:11:55,213 --> 00:12:01,935
hot er genumen tsunoyfgerukt tsvey shteyner, holts hot nisht gefelt, er hot shoyn aroyfgeshtelt a tepl oyf di shteyner, er hot shoyn gekokht.

145
00:12:03,595 --> 00:12:07,183
ales, kimat a sakh, nakher nor nisht ikh.

146
00:12:09,366 --> 00:12:14,338
un mayn froy flegt arumgeyn un betn m'zol gebn a tepl esn farn kind.

147
00:12:15,846 --> 00:12:18,944
eyne hobn gegibn, eyne hobn nisht gevolt gibn.

148
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:27,450
eyn mol zogt mayn froy tsu mir, "gey du bet." zog ikh, "ikh ken nisht. vos zol ikh tun?"

149
00:12:28,603 --> 00:12:30,925
ikh hob genumen punkt UNK in eynem,

150
00:12:31,472 --> 00:12:35,178
un ikh hob im gezogt, "efsher kent ir mir opshporn a lefl esn farn kind?"

151
00:12:36,552 --> 00:12:42,350
nisht gevolt gibn. bin ikh avekgegangen a tsebrokhener.

152
00:12:43,437 --> 00:12:44,612
vos tut men do?

153
00:12:47,250 --> 00:12:50,096
geven ze'mir oyf a barg, a FLATer,

154
00:12:50,625 --> 00:12:53,099
nor do vu s'hot zikh geendikt der barg

155
00:12:53,832 --> 00:12:57,878
bin ikh tsugegangen. khozhe der komendant hot gehitn m'zol nisht geyn ergets,

156
00:12:57,878 --> 00:13:02,553
ober ikh hob zikh shoyn adurkh geganvet, un ikh hob aropgekukt vos dortn iz.

157
00:13:02,553 --> 00:13:07,764
ze ikh az s'geyt a roykh fun a koymen. voynt dokh dortn ver.

158
00:13:07,922 --> 00:13:10,616
un ikh geb zikh a glitsh arop fun dem barg arop.

159
00:13:12,073 --> 00:13:16,404
ikh kum tsu tsum ershtn hoyz, ikh klap on,

160
00:13:17,575 --> 00:13:20,904
zi hot moyre tsu efenen di tir. ikh klap nokh a mol on,

161
00:13:20,904 --> 00:13:24,352
kumt aroys a froy, efnt oyf a shtikele di tir,

162
00:13:25,658 --> 00:13:29,162
ikh zog tsu zi, bet ikh ir, gib mir a trink vaser.

163
00:13:30,653 --> 00:13:35,692
dertseylt zi mir az m- m'hot gezogt do ku- iz ongekumen mentshn zenen mit herner,

164
00:13:36,205 --> 00:13:41,396
yidn zenen mit herner un zey bagan- ganven un dos, dos zi hot moyre.

165
00:13:41,993 --> 00:13:46,206
zog ikh zi, nisht keyner hot nisht keyn herner, un keyner ganvet nisht.

166
00:13:47,562 --> 00:13:49,918
zi hot mir aroysgegebn a bisl vaser.

167
00:13:50,987 --> 00:13:55,908
zog ikh, "efsher voltstu mir gevolt farkoyfn a tsvey POTATOES?"

168
00:13:57,315 --> 00:14:00,059
zogt zi, in hoyz arayn lozt zi nisht arayn.

169
00:14:00,555 --> 00:14:03,299
"vart tsu, mayn man kumt bald onkumen."

170
00:14:04,993 --> 00:14:08,935
der iz ongekumen. ikh hob mit im geredt.

171
00:14:09,027 --> 00:14:12,126
ikh hob im dertseylt vos an emen mayn lage un azoy vayter.

172
00:14:13,144 --> 00:14:17,356
zogt er tsu mir azoy. "na dikh a BO- na dir a BOTTLE milkh,"

173
00:14:19,894 --> 00:14:22,706
un er hot mir gegebn epes a por POTATOES,

174
00:14:22,948 --> 00:14:28,899
fun gortn, er hot gehat lebn zikh a gortn, er hot aroysgerisn tsvey tsibeles, er hot mir gegibn.

175
00:14:29,260 --> 00:14:34,772
un zogt tsu mir azoy. "m'vet aykh tseshikn in farshidene punktn arayn."

176
00:14:35,115 --> 00:14:39,964
s'do a punkt numer zeks, s'do a punkt numer tsvelf,

177
00:14:39,964 --> 00:14:44,039
s'do a punkt akhtsn, s'do a punkt fir un tsvontsik,

178
00:14:44,039 --> 00:14:47,461
s'do a punkt, nokh epes a punkt, ikh gedenk nisht genoy dem NUMBER.

179
00:14:47,603 --> 00:14:49,234
"vet men tseshikn aykh.

180
00:14:49,847 --> 00:14:57,631
dortn hobn gevoynt di geshlosene fun zibn un draysikstn in yor. zey hobn men avekgeshikt vayter un ir vet darfn

181
00:14:57,631 --> 00:15:05,231
farnemen di pletser. vu m'vet aykh veln shikn, zolst dikh oysbahaltn. zolst nisht forn.

182
00:15:05,845 --> 00:15:10,512
un az vest hern az m'vil shikn oyf punkt numer eyns, do zolstu forn.

183
00:15:12,156 --> 00:15:18,444
ikh nem iber dem magazin dortn, WE WILL DO BUSINESS."

184
00:15:20,965 --> 00:15:23,425
ikh bin krik aroyf un shtel dikh der-

185
00:15:23,425 --> 00:15:31,286
derfreyt farn kind a bisl milkh, un un zey m'shaft shoyn tsunoyf epes a tepl mit farsh- m'kokht shoyn di POTATO.

186
00:15:33,992 --> 00:15:36,821
vu m'shikt, m'bahalt zikh oys.

187
00:15:38,498 --> 00:15:42,120
teyl hot men shoyn avekgeshikt, ober di MOST iz nokh do do.

188
00:15:43,729 --> 00:15:45,748
darf men forn nokh broyt.

189
00:15:45,754 --> 00:15:50,473
broyt iz nishto do, m'darf forn s'bay a finef mayl,

190
00:15:50,597 --> 00:15:58,744
fort men mit a mit a TRUCK, der komendant fort, un m'nemt fun dortn broyt. keyner vil nisht forn.

191
00:15:58,744 --> 00:16:04,934
s'do eyn un zibetsik kinder, un keyn eyn elter vil nisht forn mitn komendant nokh broyt.

192
00:16:05,211 --> 00:16:10,723
Yizak, ikh bin do. aroyf oyfn TRUCK, m'fort avek.

193
00:16:11,556 --> 00:16:20,916
azoy vi m'kumt tsu forn krik, mitn broyt, iz nishto keyn lebediker nefesh. ale zenen tseforn.

194
00:16:21,428 --> 00:16:26,737
mayn froy, mitn kind, un ikh shtey mit tsvey zek broyt.

195
00:16:27,874 --> 00:16:29,710
vu hin zenen zey geforn vu ahin?

196
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:33,178
zogt men shoyn, zenen geforn oyf fir un tsvontsikstn utshastok.

197
00:16:33,178 --> 00:16:34,719
fir un tsvontsikstn punkt, s'vert mir nisht gut.

198
00:16:37,307 --> 00:16:40,997
ober ikh far- di kinder zenen dokh on broyt.

199
00:16:42,032 --> 00:16:49,570
ikh bet zikh barn komendant m'hey- m'shaft shoyn a a vagonetke vos geyt oyf reder, m'dershlept zikh dortn ahin.

200
00:16:50,689 --> 00:16:56,339
dortn di vos zenen geforn frier hobn farnumen tsimern fun di geshlosene,

201
00:16:56,339 --> 00:17:00,431
holts hot nisht gefelt, m'hot ayngeheytst, s'geven varem,

202
00:17:00,431 --> 00:17:03,508
zey hobn shoyn gehat vos tsu kokhn, mit dem mit mayns gesheft.

203
00:17:03,582 --> 00:17:07,271
un mayn froy zitst in droysn un veynt mit bitere trern.

204
00:17:07,665 --> 00:17:12,890
zi hot nisht vu arayntsugeyn. "vos dernemstu zikh bloyz mit gornishe gesheftn?

205
00:17:13,521 --> 00:17:16,867
zey ale hobn hobn nisht gekent geyn keyner nisht nor du?

206
00:17:16,867 --> 00:17:19,922
un vos zol ikh t- yetst tun? mit ikh hob nisht vu arayntsugeyn."

207
00:17:19,922 --> 00:17:25,309
un dos iz shoyn gevezn dos iz shoyn gevezn

208
00:17:26,936 --> 00:17:37,916
ende oygust, azoy mitl oygust, ende oygust, s'geven kalt. Sibir! nisht gut!

209
00:17:38,884 --> 00:17:44,277
zog ikh in komendant, "ikh bin mit a kleyn kind, vos tut men?"

210
00:17:44,723 --> 00:17:46,961
vayzt er mir on oyf a hayzkele,

211
00:17:47,895 --> 00:17:54,301
ikh gey arayn un di vent zenen ofene. zogt er, "vest nemen breter, farklapn m'vet makhn a a KITCHEN do."

212
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:58,335
zog ikh, "vu do vel ikh do gefroyrn vern mitn kind, vos redstu?"

213
00:18:01,918 --> 00:18:05,692
"du vest geyn mit mir oyfn ershtn utshastok." fun ershtn punkt.

214
00:18:07,116 --> 00:18:13,725
un er kloybt oys tsen FAMILIES. azoy mer veyniker mer mentshlekhe.

215
00:18:14,288 --> 00:18:18,467
vayl s'dokh geven a rov, s'geven mentshn farshidnartike.

216
00:18:20,295 --> 00:18:25,588
ANYWAY, m'hot di nakht ibergezesn,

217
00:18:26,151 --> 00:18:30,515
un in der fri iz geven a fur un ikh hob oyfgezetst di froy mitn kind,

218
00:18:31,905 --> 00:18:36,303
un un nokh andere. un der komendant zogt, "du kum mit mir nokhn vald.

219
00:18:36,613 --> 00:18:40,944
az m'vet geyn nokhn vald vet zayn kirtserer veg, mir veln mir zayn frier vi zey."

220
00:18:42,756 --> 00:18:48,403
m'iz gegangen iz men ongekumen oyfn plats dortn, hobn di geshlosene, ven zenen geven yorn,

221
00:18:48,409 --> 00:18:53,500
hobn zey oyfgeboyt fun holts a HOSPITAL, geven akht tsimern,

222
00:18:53,674 --> 00:18:58,041
prekhtik, mit gem- mit gefarbte FLOORS, mit mayses.

223
00:18:58,041 --> 00:19:03,472
ikh bin arayn, farnumen a tsimer, ikh hob nokh arayngebrengt a shenkl, dos un dortn,

224
00:19:03,597 --> 00:19:05,312
ikh hob epes gehat a por tsent bay zikh,

225
00:19:05,352 --> 00:19:07,995
bin ikh geven in droysn, eyder zey zenen ongekumen,

226
00:19:08,052 --> 00:19:13,161
iz geshtanen a kristin, un ikh hob bay ir gekoyft epes a bisl milkh,

227
00:19:13,161 --> 00:19:17,613
a por POTATOES, un zi hot gehat shvomen. MUSHROOMS.

228
00:19:19,358 --> 00:19:24,212
un do hob ikh shoyn gezukht, hob ikh shoyn gefunen a tepl, a dos, mayses, ikh kokh shoyn.

229
00:19:27,120 --> 00:19:31,231
un in shank ikh hob oyfgehongen mayn mantl mitn SUIT mit mayses gesheftn,

230
00:19:31,812 --> 00:19:36,143
zey zenen ongekumen. mayn mayn froy iz ongekumen, zi iz geven farshtendlekh zi iz geven tsufridn.

231
00:19:36,351 --> 00:19:42,926
s'nokh gevezn a COUPLE vos er hot gevolt arayngebn a pa- zayn's a mantl tsu mir in CUPBOARD arayn, breng arayn.

232
00:19:45,227 --> 00:19:52,832
bay nakht, m'iz gegangen shlofn, zogt der komendant az do tor men nisht farmakh- farmakhn keyn tirn. ale tirn darfn zayn ofn.

233
00:19:55,605 --> 00:19:58,214
ikh hob im nisht gedorfn folgn? ikh hob gedorfn farmakhn?

234
00:20:00,330 --> 00:20:06,045
un er hot zikh oyfgekhapt in mitn der nakht hob ikh derhert az men geyt ver aroys fun tsimer.

235
00:20:07,131 --> 00:20:08,239
s'hot zikh mir gedokhtn.

236
00:20:11,147 --> 00:20:13,675
ikh gey arop fun bet, ikh geb a kuk arayn in CUPBOARD arayn,

237
00:20:13,675 --> 00:20:18,060
iz dem fraynt vos er hot arayngenumen zayn mantl, er hot gehongen in der front, ze ikh az dos mantl hengt.

238
00:20:20,597 --> 00:20:26,025
shpeter tsu az s'gevorn azoy arum akht a zeyger, her ikh a gevalt, m'hot im baganvet, dem baga-

239
00:20:26,757 --> 00:20:28,742
ikh gey nokh a mol tsu tsum CUPBOARD.

240
00:20:28,748 --> 00:20:35,306
dem fraynt's pel- mantl hengt, mayn's hot men tsu geganvet. a SUIT un dem m'hot tsu geganvet.

241
00:20:37,118 --> 00:20:42,950
shoyn vayter baganvet. oy biter iz biter, ikh hob gepanikt.

242
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,223
vifl tsayt zent ir dort gevezn?

243
00:20:43,902 --> 00:20:44,858
ANYWAY,

244
00:20:45,193 --> 00:20:45,903
vi?

245
00:20:45,223 --> 00:20:47,945
vifl tsayt zent ir dort gez- gevezn?

246
00:20:48,036 --> 00:20:50,308
vifl tsayt?

247
00:20:48,195 --> 00:20:49,355
velkhe tsayt?

248
00:20:49,909 --> 00:20:52,603
dortn? m'iz dortn geblibn.

249
00:20:50,567 --> 00:20:51,405
yo.

250
00:20:52,373 --> 00:20:53,510
di gantse tsay-

251
00:20:52,744 --> 00:20:55,505
ober m'hot aroysgetribn fun HOSPITAL.

252
00:20:55,512 --> 00:20:58,898
derlebn HOSPITAL iz geshtanen hayzkelekh azelkhe di kleyne.

253
00:20:59,916 --> 00:21:02,019
hayzke m'hot gekent adurkh kukn dos.

254
00:21:02,211 --> 00:21:05,074
ANYWAY, ikh hob gekrign a hayzkele lebn HOSPITAL.

255
00:21:06,008 --> 00:21:09,869
m'iz arayn dortn un mayn froy iz nisht geven fun di foyle,

256
00:21:09,869 --> 00:21:13,173
zi hot bald gezen tsu farshtupn ale lekher mit mayns gesheft.

257
00:21:13,213 --> 00:21:20,092
az der komendant flegt zogn az zol nemen di mentshn, di andere zoln nemen a bayshpil vi rayn s'iz bay mir.

258
00:21:21,415 --> 00:21:27,298
SO m'iz arayn do aher. s'ongekumen a dokter.

259
00:21:27,355 --> 00:21:33,106
dem dokter hot men gedorfn brengen, mikh hot men tsugeteylt tsu transport.

260
00:21:33,106 --> 00:21:35,280
m'hot mir gegebn a ferd un vogn,

261
00:21:35,286 --> 00:21:39,223
un m'hot gedorf- vos m'hot gedorfn forn brengen, dos hob hob ikh gedorfn.

262
00:21:39,223 --> 00:21:40,966
s'geven nokh etlekhene azelkhe.

263
00:21:42,137 --> 00:21:46,586
hob ikh gedorfn forn nokh dem dokter, zeks kilometer tsu brengen dem dokter.

264
00:21:47,267 --> 00:21:49,505
nu farshtendlekh ikh hob gebrengt dem dokter,

265
00:21:50,457 --> 00:21:56,188
un un dortn in HOSPITAL iz nokh nisht geven tsugegreyt altsding, hob ikh im arayngenumen iz er geshlofn bay mir oykhet.

266
00:21:57,460 --> 00:22:00,660
vos iz geven mayn kavone az er zol shlofn bay mir?

267
00:22:01,273 --> 00:22:06,026
er vet dokh darfn hobn a NURSE. zol er araynnemen mayn vayb far a NURSE.

268
00:22:06,437 --> 00:22:10,464
un azoy iz geven. er hot ir arayngenumen far a NURSE.

269
00:22:13,153 --> 00:22:17,884
ANYWAY, dos kind hot men arayngenumen in a

270
00:22:17,884 --> 00:22:21,568
kinder, bay tog iz zi gegangen in a in a in a kinder HOME dortn.

271
00:22:23,143 --> 00:22:28,183
eyn mol kumt zi tsu geyn, un di kleyne moyd, un veynt. vos veynstu?

272
00:22:28,206 --> 00:22:33,937
s'tut ir vey di finger. zi hot zikh epes farshtokhn dem finger.

273
00:22:35,918 --> 00:22:39,050
nu, efsher oysveykn mit heyse vaser, vet vos.

274
00:22:41,082 --> 00:22:45,800
s'vert nakht. s'vert fintster bay nakht, shtil.

275
00:22:45,992 --> 00:22:52,247
ikh gib a kuk, geyen tsvey royte pasn do o. tsvey. POISON.

276
00:22:53,974 --> 00:22:56,448
un ikh ze az dos geyt azoy un dos geyt shnel.

277
00:22:57,602 --> 00:23:00,043
ikh loyf arayn nor tsum dokter, ikh zog, "dokter,

278
00:23:00,606 --> 00:23:04,380
k- kum arayn gib a kuk dos kind zen az s'geyt do azelkhe tsvey royte pasn!"

279
00:23:04,673 --> 00:23:07,249
o! get er a kum arayn, get er a kuk,

280
00:23:07,373 --> 00:23:11,670
zo- zogt er, az m'vet gornisht tun, dos kind vet oysgeyn. biz in der fri vet es nisht oyshaltn.

281
00:23:12,570 --> 00:23:18,707
zi vet farPOISONt vern. un er shteyt un er zogt mir, "vos ken ikh tun? ikh hob nisht keyn meditsinen.

282
00:23:19,557 --> 00:23:26,742
ikh hob gornisht vos tsu tun." shteyt un trakht un loyft nokh arayn krik in HOSPITAL arayn.

283
00:23:26,742 --> 00:23:30,486
un kumt krik tsu loyfn mit a tsvengl. ir veyst vos a tsvengl iz?

284
00:23:32,685 --> 00:23:37,370
un er zogt tsu mir, "nem dos kind oyf der hant. un halt dem finger."

285
00:23:37,798 --> 00:23:43,732
un git a khap on in nogl, ikh hob gemeynt dos kind geyt im aroys fun di hent.

286
00:23:43,958 --> 00:23:47,296
un s'hot gegebn a shprits aroys di di shmuts,

287
00:23:47,296 --> 00:23:50,128
un azoy vi er hot aroysgerisn azoy hot ongehoybn tsu geyn krik.

288
00:23:52,446 --> 00:23:55,261
un farshtendlekh er hot gemakht a bandazh un azoy vayter,

289
00:23:55,261 --> 00:23:58,734
un dos kind un zitst in bet azoy zol UNK,

290
00:23:59,230 --> 00:24:05,315
vi zi zogt oyf rusish, zogt zi tsu im azoy, "UNK. vi lebstu, mayn fingerl?"

291
00:24:09,287 --> 00:24:12,943
m'iz opgeven dortn zibetsn monatn.

292
00:24:17,843 --> 00:24:24,485
ikh hob gedorfn krign loyt mayn arbet zeks zibn hundert rubl a monat.

293
00:24:24,778 --> 00:24:28,113
hob ikh gekrign zeks un zibetsik rubl a monat.

294
00:24:29,149 --> 00:24:33,390
ikh hob gezen epes m'nart mikh op, m'baganvet mikh fun kop biz fus.

295
00:24:35,629 --> 00:24:37,800
bin ikh gegangen, ikh hob gemakht a PAPER.

296
00:24:37,958 --> 00:24:42,659
vos ikh hob gefirt hob ikh farshribn dem INVOICE, velkhn tog, vifl,

297
00:24:42,666 --> 00:24:48,144
zey hobn getsolt epes fir rubl fun a ton, vifl ton UNK. a gantsn monat.

298
00:24:48,201 --> 00:24:52,295
ikh hob unterges- gekhasmet hob ikh gezen ikh darf krign akht hundert rubl.

299
00:24:52,487 --> 00:24:54,433
akht hundert rubl, ikh ken khotsh,

300
00:24:54,433 --> 00:24:58,033
ikh hob nisht gehat far vos oystsukoyfn a gantser monat keyn broyt.

301
00:24:58,883 --> 00:25:03,652
un undz hot men getsolt far der arbet, undz hobn gedorfn koyfn dos esn. dos esn.

302
00:25:04,198 --> 00:25:09,283
ANYWAY, m'kumt arayn nokh nokh di WAGES,

303
00:25:09,283 --> 00:25:12,444
bay di END OF MONTH, ikh hob dos PAPER, ikh vayz nisht gornisht,

304
00:25:13,092 --> 00:25:15,398
get men mir zeks un zibetsik rubl.

305
00:25:16,399 --> 00:25:21,897
ikh hob nisht gevust az groyser ofitsir, fun di po- a N.K.V.D.,

306
00:25:21,897 --> 00:25:25,202
iz ongekumen, er zitst in tsveytn tsimer. ikh hob nisht gevust.

307
00:25:25,478 --> 00:25:30,385
un azoy vi m'hot m'hot mir gegebn di zeks un zibetsik rubl, ikh bin geshtanen bay a tish,

308
00:25:30,385 --> 00:25:35,900
hob ikh gegebn aza min klap in tish un ikh hob gegebn a geshrey, "ganovim! ir baganvet mikh!"

309
00:25:36,328 --> 00:25:39,781
iz gevorn a geshrey azoy azoy vi ikh hob oyfgeregt.

310
00:25:39,973 --> 00:25:47,173
git zikh an efn oyf a tir, un der hoykher ofitsir shteyt in di tir, "un ver makht dem skandal?"

311
00:25:47,837 --> 00:25:52,438
far a skandal krigstu tsvey yor. loytn gezets.

312
00:25:52,984 --> 00:25:58,901
zog ikh, ikh. zogt er, "du? UNK kum nor arayn do aher.

313
00:26:00,696 --> 00:26:02,597
far vos hostu gemakht dem skandal?"

314
00:26:03,666 --> 00:26:06,984
un der komendant hob ikh im gemakht im gemakht a BLOUSE.

315
00:26:07,041 --> 00:26:11,929
nor keyn gelt farshtendlekh nisht genumen bay im. un er iz oykh dortn gevezn.

316
00:26:13,015 --> 00:26:17,969
zog ikh, "m'baganvet mikh yedn monat. un ikh hob nisht gevust.

317
00:26:18,111 --> 00:26:21,260
ikh hob gevust ikh darf krign mer, nor m'hot mir nisht gegebn."

318
00:26:21,655 --> 00:26:24,163
ikh nem aroys dos PAPER, zog ikh, "na a kuk.

319
00:26:24,490 --> 00:26:29,833
hostu dem tog, hostu di date, host dem numer fun dem INVOICE,

320
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:36,127
host a gantsn monat, ze unter ze azoy o. un ikh krig zeks un zibetsik rubl?"

321
00:26:37,365 --> 00:26:43,012
zogt er, "nem di zeks un zibetsik rubl. gey aheym. I WILL LOOK AFTER THIS."

322
00:26:44,487 --> 00:26:49,391
ANYWAY, ikh bin ave- aheymgegangen,

323
00:26:49,954 --> 00:26:54,330
tsu morgns, ikh fleg geyn zeyer fri dortn vu di ferd zenen geshtanen

324
00:26:54,330 --> 00:26:59,938
aynshpanen, ikh hob gevolt forn, ikh hob gevolt zayn Stakhanovets. a guter arbetorer a groyser.

325
00:27:00,552 --> 00:27:06,047
bin ikh gegangen zeyer fri. ruft men mikh in OFFICE arayn.

326
00:27:07,217 --> 00:27:11,093
vos iz? zey hobn mir gefunen nokh dray hundert rubl.

327
00:27:13,579 --> 00:27:18,973
NO. ikh nem di dray hundert rubl NO, s'felt gelt.

328
00:27:21,443 --> 00:27:30,600
ikh gey krik fun dortn farn azoy mitog tsayt, zogt men, m'hot gefunen nokh fir hundert rubl. shoyn zibn.

329
00:27:31,888 --> 00:27:33,839
zog ikh, s'felt mir nokh hundert rubl.

330
00:27:35,078 --> 00:27:37,704
un FINALLY, di hundert rubl iz shoyn farfaln gevorn.

331
00:27:39,482 --> 00:27:44,657
un do hot zikh untergerukt di milkhome farshtendlekh.

332
00:27:46,266 --> 00:27:50,344
un m'hot mikh avekgenumen, mikh mit nokh etlekhene,

333
00:27:50,502 --> 00:27:55,761
hot men mikh avekgenumen azoy bay a draysik mayl avek fun di froy,

334
00:27:56,593 --> 00:28:01,802
in a plats arayn vu m'darf hakn dem vald, un s'iz a groyser barg,

335
00:28:02,027 --> 00:28:09,446
un zey geyen BUILDn a a AIRPORT, az di di di eroplanen zenen kenen aruntergeyn untern barg arunter.

336
00:28:11,967 --> 00:28:15,926
zey hobn undz dervegns nisht oysgetsolt damolts, nisht gehat oysgetsolt.

337
00:28:17,248 --> 00:28:28,026
un dortn shteyen tsvey kukhn militerishe, an orkester shpilt, m'firt undz tsu der arbet, un fun der arbet.

338
00:28:31,052 --> 00:28:35,855
ANYWAY, shlofn shloft men in dortn in aza min shayer.

339
00:28:37,363 --> 00:28:41,779
esn ken men krign fun kesl, m'darf koyfn. nor keyn gelt hot men nisht.

340
00:28:42,274 --> 00:28:46,690
hot men gemakht a STRIKE. m'geyt nisht tsu der arbet.

341
00:28:48,265 --> 00:28:52,815
s'ongekumen a a, dakht zikh mir es iz geven a yid, a a kapitan,

342
00:28:53,226 --> 00:28:59,041
un er zogt, loytn gezets ken men aykh mishpetn militerish unter a militerishn gerikht,

343
00:28:59,132 --> 00:29:05,235
az m'ken aykh oder ir kent geyn UNK tfise oder m'ken aykh shisn, vayl s'iz milkhome.

344
00:29:06,388 --> 00:29:11,073
"mir viln geyn, gib mir esn! mir viln geyn tsu der arbet!

345
00:29:11,721 --> 00:29:14,955
ober geb geb undz es- zey hobn undz nisht oysgetsolt."

346
00:29:15,450 --> 00:29:20,425
